data.description: Welcome to the neighborhood of Stone Cliff Acres.  This 3 bedroom / 2 bath ranch style home is situated on a lovely level to rolling 1.03 acre lot. The home is nicely set back off the road for added privacy with established fruit trees. Enjoy the open floor plan with cathedral ceiling and stone-stacked fireplace. 2 washer and dryer hookups. 2 car garage and shed. IN HOME SECURITY SYSTEM for safety and to ease your mind while working or traveling. THIS IS A GREAT STARTER HOME WITH PLENTY OF YARD - ENJOY THE OUTDOORS and MAKE MEMORIES. **Measurements are estimated. All information is to be verified and buyers are to perform due diligence.***
